stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to begin.

In this experiment, three images of people will appear in the center of the screen.

Your task is to rank these images based on how real you think they are.

The ranking level is between 1 to 3, with 1 representing the most realistic one and 3 the least realistic one.

There are totally 100 groups of images. The time to rank is not limited.

When you finish one group, click the Continue button to continue to the next one.

At the end of the experiment, your name and age will be asked and recorded.
You have reached the end of the experiment! Press any key to finish.
